

<div class="span10 offset1">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
  </div>
  <h4>Welcome <%= @candidate.firstname %>! Please read carefully before proceeding...</h4><br />
  <ul>
    <li>This test contains <strong> Total <%= @total_ques %> Questions.</strong></li>
    <li>Questions can be answered by selecting the appropriate button (<input type="radio"/>) next to the options.</li>
    <li>You can scroll to a certain question quickly by clicking on the question's button in the <em>Question Navigation</em> section.
    <li>Answered questions will be marked in green in both the <em>question number</em> and in the <em>Questions Navigation</em> section.</li>
